@host = http://localhost:3000/api
@userId = 2f5e7c1a-9c6d-4b4b-8e2a-1234567890ab

### Listar usuarios con filtros y paginaci√≥n
GET {{host}}/users?page=1&limit=20&search=ana&sort=name&dir=asc&role=moderator&active=true
Accept: application/json

### Obtener un usuario por id
GET {{host}}/users/{{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### Crear un nuevo usuario
POST {{host}}/users
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Ana Marques",
  "email": "ana.marques@example.com",
  "roles": [
    "moderator",
    "editor"
  ],
  "active": true,
  "password": "Secret123!"
}

### Actualizar un usuario (reemplazo completo)
PUT {{host}}/users/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Ana Marques",
  "email": "ana.marques@example.com",
  "roles": [
    "moderator"
  ],
  "active": false,
  "password": "NewSecret456!"
}

### Eliminar un usuario
DELETE {{host}}/users/{{userId}}

### Actualizar solo el estado activo del usuario
PATCH {{host}}/users/{{userId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "active": true
}
